      "id": "69ac15506efe6171bb6fecf6",
      "text": "カルサリカンニ",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1772885329,
      "updated": 1772885329
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac15500000000000be2cd5",
      "text": "from [2025/04/27]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1772885329,
      "updated": 1772885329
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac15500000000000be2cd7",
      "text": "という語を知った。[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1772885329,
      "updated": 1772885336
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac15500000000000be2cd8",
      "text": "\tKalsarikännit",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1772885329,
      "updated": 1772885334
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac15500000000000be2cd9",
      "text": " 「下着姿で一人で酔っ払うこと」を意味する[フィンランド]語",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1772885329,
      "updated": 1772885334
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac15500000000000be2cda",
      "text": " \t直訳は「[下着酔っ払い]」",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1772885329,
      "updated": 1772885334
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac15500000000000be2cdb",
      "text": " [https://finland.fi/emoji/kalsarikannit/ Kalsarikännit - thisisFINLAND]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1772885329,
      "updated": 1772885334
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac15500000000000be2cdc",
      "text": " 語のテンポ感というか響きがいい感じなんで、なんかのタイトルに使えそう。ボドゲとか。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1772885329,
      "updated": 1772885334
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac15500000000000be2cdd",
      "text": "  [カルカソンヌ]っぽい[cak.icon][inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1772885329,
      "updated": 1772885334
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac15500000000000be2cde",
      "text": "  [ミープル]がパンツ一丁で草原に寝転がってそうだ笑[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1772885329,
      "updated": 1772885346
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac15500000000000be2cdf",
      "text": "  ミープルは実は全裸()[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1772885329,
      "updated": 1772885334
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac15500000000000be2ce0",
      "text": "  \t[https://gyazo.com/272d6078d54a236b2c820934ef05f50b]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1772885329,
      "updated": 1772885334
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac15500000000000be2ce1",
